@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@serviceOrderCode = 1
@serviceOrderNumber = OS-1774544009950
@userCode = 1

### Finish service order
### This action performs the stock output for product items
### Optionally inform payment data to create a receipt during finish
### Use serviceOrderCode in the URL. serviceOrderNumber is only the visible OS number.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/service-orders/{{serviceOrderCode}}/finish
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "changedByCode": "{{userCode}}",
  "receiptAmount": 100.00,
  "paymentMethod": "PIX",
  "receiptNotes": "Pagamento recebido na finalizacao",
  "receivedByCode": "{{userCode}}",
  "notes": "Servico finalizado e pronto para retirada"
}
